name: WhatIsMyPoolTemperature
0: ”Alexa, ask my pool what is my pool temperature?”
skdetail:
Rated: Guidance Suggested. This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: my pool
des: This skill interactives with a data logger service such as io.adafruit.com. You'll need a device that logs data to this service. Right now, the ability to customize the endpoint is not available so you'll only get my pool's temperature. When this is released, you'll be able to connect Alexa to your data feed so you can get your specific details.
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
